{"tid":1549464,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[美軍來了我來路] 美國國歌挑機","createTime":"2019-09-07T10:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T12:39:13.000Z","uid":66049,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d34264af2b0f836a253551170521325cd66942af","tid":1549464,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日咁重要點可以唔識唱美國國歌呢？</span><br />\n唔識就要聽下，背埋歌詞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M1wLtAXDgqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM1wLtAXDgqg&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=d96c982e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M1wLtAXDgqg</a><br />\n<br />\n但唱國歌並要唔係鄰國咁樣一式一樣咁難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果俾揀，一定係聽Lady Gaga 喺Super Bowl嘅演唱<br />\n2:44 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Lady Gaga 心諗 nailed it! </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GbXSZBnBOQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGbXSZBnBOQ4&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=3021cf69\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GbXSZBnBOQ4</a><br />\n<br />\n雖則可以唔同人唔同演繹，但呢個絕對唔好學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CMA2iF6RuXk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCMA2iF6RuXk&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=dd731485\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CMA2iF6RuXk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後就算你識唔識唱都好，美國幫咗我地好多好多，聽日遮打見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"017ec8acf59bab09f7f08ddcb951beb760ceaee3","tid":1549464,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"屌打錯字<br />\n美軍來了我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">帶</span></strong></span>路"},{"pid":"0ea5a08557f642094b737ff04cc3fc172041c4e4","tid":1549464,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"要有旗海"},{"pid":"088a7349814fd984f05163a60fd7c073410498cf","tid":1549464,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"Oh, say can you see"},{"pid":"91766db1b122e7e7e318428189e38de5dcf612c9","tid":1549464,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"元朗9.9七點半有人鏈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dQdQeS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dQdQeS</a>"},{"pid":"43bccd0df16f576319c070e433eb63fe0a9137ec","tid":1549464,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb146ff7f1dee265f557eb361866dc46552c40d","tid":1549464,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"088a7349814fd984f05163a60fd7c073410498cf","tid":1549464,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"Oh, say can you see"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"by the dawn's early li